{"service_name": "CESG CCSC Security Audit and Review", "service_id": "7805932744435640", "company_name": "Info-Assure LTD", "page_content": "<main id=\"content\" role=\"main\">\n <div class=\"grid-row\">\n  <div class=\"column-two-thirds\">\n   <header class=\"page-heading-smaller\">\n    <p class=\"context\">\n     Info-Assure LTD\n    </p>\n    <h1>\n     CESG CCSC Security Audit and Review\n    </h1>\n   </header>\n  </div>\n </div>\n <div class=\"grid-row\">\n  <div class=\"column-two-thirds\">\n   <p class=\"service-summary-lede\">\n    IA audits; reviewing security policy documentation.  ISO/IEC 27001 Lead Auditors, CCP IA Auditors, PCI-DSS QSA, IRCA qualified lead auditor. Auditing ISO27001 and ISO22301\r\nProcess audit and policy review of key policies and procedures, identifying any missing policies or any requiring updates, according to the client\u2019s security requirements and their environment.\n   </p>\n   <h2 class=\"service-summary-heading\">\n    Features\n   </h2>\n   <ul class=\"service-summary-features-and-benefits\">\n    <li>\n     Comprehensive information security audits, assessments and gap analysis\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Standards based e.g. ISO27001, Baseline Control Set\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Compliance security audits, addressing applicable legislative regulatory compliance\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Service assurance assessments, to prepare for third-party audits\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Internal audits of organisation\u2019s Information Security Management System\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Technical security assessments, focused on technical controls\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Business continuity and physical security assessments and audits.\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n   <h2 class=\"service-summary-heading\">\n    Benefits\n   </h2>\n   <ul class=\"service-summary-features-and-benefits\">\n    <li>\n     Led by CCP-qualified IA Auditors, ISO27001 Lead Auditors.\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Highly experienced UK-based senior consultants, specialising in the public sector.\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Proven methodologies and document templates to support rapid, successful certification.\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Pragmatic advice, tailored to the context of client\u2019s business needs.\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Clients can make an informed decision on appropriate risk treatment.\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Reduced risk of delays as resource made available as required.\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     As CCP-qualified Consultants, we are aware of Government security requirements.\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     As independent information security specialists, we provide unbiased services.\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     ISO 27001 and 9001 certified, with all reports independently reviewed.\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Increased compliance, whilst reducing risks to reputation damage\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"column-one-third\">\n   <div id=\"meta\">\n    <h2 class=\"visuallyhidden\">\n     Pricing\n    </h2>\n    <p class=\"price\">\n     \u00a3720 to \u00a3900 per person per day\n    </p>\n    <ul class=\"price-caveats\">\n     <li>\n      Excluding VAT\n     </li>\n     <li>\n      Minimum contract period: Day\n     </li>\n    </ul>\n    <h2 class=\"visuallyhidden\">\n     Service documents\n    </h2>\n    <ul class=\"document-list\">\n     <li class=\"document-list-item\">\n      <a class=\"document-link-with-icon\" href=\"https://assets.digitalmarketplace.service.gov.uk/g-cloud-7/documents/92291/7805932744435640-pricing-document-2015-10-05-1635.pdf\">\n       <span class=\"document-icon\">\n        pdf\n        <span>\n         document:\n        </span>\n       </span>\n       Pricing\n      </a>\n     </li>\n     <li class=\"document-list-item\">\n      <a class=\"document-link-with-icon\" href=\"https://assets.digitalmarketplace.service.gov.uk/g-cloud-7/documents/92291/7805932744435640-sfia-rate-card-2015-10-05-1635.pdf\">\n       <span class=\"document-icon\">\n        pdf\n        <s